title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 5 categories of Country on the x axis representing 2 groups: Yes, and No.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Country Northern Ireland with a mean value of 50.0.
The lowest category is observed at Wales that has a mean value of 49.5
In case of Scotland, Yes shows more dominance than any other Country with a value 84.0 and it has the lowest value 66.0 in Wales.
